# Plan data migrations

When this rule applies, read and follow [`.cursor/skills/data-format-migration/SKILL.md`](../skills/data-format-migration/SKILL.md) **before** editing.

- Bump `PERMAPLANNER_FILE_VERSION` and add a migration step for every persisted shape change.
- Keep `version` on local monolithic saves and on all three GitHub shard files.
- Add or update tests in `permaplannerFileMigrate.test.ts`; run related unit tests after changes.
